{"tid":2437730,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"八方(歧路)旅人的BOSS戰鬥音樂轉接真係好撚勁","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T15:00:05.000Z","uid":180561,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ae3c7afd3f7d9aaf38049c34e024c6dbdbd1bb","tid":2437730,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b7Zc3f8cPnU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb7Zc3f8cPnU&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=dd3225ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b7Zc3f8cPnU</a><br />\n(CC中字, 安心食用)<br />\n雖然無縫轉接音樂早在1991年的monkey island2裡, 就有因應場景而改變配樂(維持melody)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7N41TEcjcvM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7N41TEcjcvM&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=517a6f35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7N41TEcjcvM</a><br />\n但是八方旅人它的音樂轉接特色<br />\n1. 戰前劇情緊張的氣氛, 以一首不斷重複的&quot;戰前短曲&quot;醞釀情緒, 再以一個trasition(在任何時候)流暢承接以上情緒到戰鬥音樂中<br />\n2. 八位角色的主題音樂不同, 因而編寫了八首各自源用相同風格的&quot;戰前短曲&quot; 及 &quot;bridge&quot;, 以達到&quot;八首不同風格的音樂都能隨時轉接到任意四首不同的boss戰鬥音樂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQkr2bQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQkr2bQ.png&h=bcf610a7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"small\">我玩落果陣都唔覺, 但係上網發現左呢樣野果陣, 真係又幫隻作品加左分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"276f1855e11c9fd1c89ed91c690ed3036f5ddbaf","tid":2437730,"uid":136416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"j一j先<br />\n謝分享"},{"pid":"f0eb4cacf186c1319981b0da29c4374f1c082d1f","tid":2437730,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"竟然咁有巧思！！！<br />\n真係無留意到，JJJJJJJJJJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bb7236b7fb73d0c8b63dee8d2ed8b67f304c10","tid":2437730,"uid":44267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"八方真係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cfe3c375037ac0b77a2a6c1db93cef9fc7e8c7","tid":2437730,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b0gvM4q2hdI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb0gvM4q2hdI&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=bbb6421b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b0gvM4q2hdI</a><br />\n其實一啲「動態」背景音樂，有更多嘅例子喺以上嘅片入邊。但係八方旅人有佢特別嘅地方"},{"pid":"4a51afd70b0e3f35984b793a4ed0182c30739d46","tid":2437730,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Imtlj1Po9d0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FImtlj1Po9d0&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=874a2653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Imtlj1Po9d0</a><br />\n&uarr;隱藏boss戰鬥曲<br />\n無縫連接mix咗3首曲，好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600a03881fde394fe21c364fb8b6a62c512a74c","tid":2437730,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a51afd70b0e3f35984b793a4ed0182c30739d46","tid":2437730,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Imtlj1Po9d0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FImtlj1Po9d0&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=874a2653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Imtlj1Po9d0</a><br />\n&uarr;隱藏boss戰鬥曲<br />\n無縫連接mix咗3首曲，好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202